text: Kampung Bukit Lanchong is a small village in Subang Jaya, Selangor, Malaysia. The village is located between Puchong, UEP Subang Jaya (USJ), Putra Heights, Alam Megah (HICOM), Kota Kemuning and Bandar Saujana Putra.
